  "reference_number": "RUS2747",
  "remarks": "\nJSC ATLAS is an involved person under the Russia (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019 on the grounds that it is an entity involved in obtaining a benefit from or supporting the Government of Russia, because it is carrying on business in a sector of strategic significance to the Government of Russia, namely, the Russian extractives sector. \n",
